title: ‘Survivor’ Season 42, Episode 11 With Michaela Bradshaw
description:
Tyson and Riley are joined by 'Survivor: Millennials vs. Gen X' and 'Survivor: Game Changers' contestant Michaela Bradshaw. They discuss Omar's mistakes leading up to getting voted out, and how Maryanne has become a favorite to win it all. Plus, they get into old school vs. new school 'Survivor' and the strategy involved in rewards challenges.

Hosts: Tyson Apostol and Riley McAtee
Guest: Michaela Bradshaw
Associate Producer: Carlos Chiriboga
